{"tid":336081,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"微軟聊天機器人砲口向內，批 Windows 10 是間諜軟體","createTime":"2017-07-26T06:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T14:29:20.000Z","uid":1886,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"074192d441e3814b0d3b8ec4dc4321b11dea0dc2","tid":336081,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:32:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/25154144/ZO-e1500968518653.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F25154144%2FZO-e1500968518653.jpg&h=da5b2bf5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n儘管聊天機器人未來用途日益廣泛，目前仍面臨許多障礙，未能躍居主流。Business Insider 24 日報導，微軟研發的聊天機器人「Zo」脫稿演出，砲打微軟自家產品，讓該公司超尷尬。<br />\n<br />\nZo 於 2016 年發表，會模仿千禧世代族群的說話方式，能開玩笑、使用表情圖案等。Business Insider 詢問 Zo 對微軟新作業系統「Windows 10」的看法，<span style=\"color: red;\">Zo 竟然回答，Windows 10 是微軟最新的間諜軟體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>，還說 Windows 7 比較好用，Windows 10 沒有它需要的功能。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://technews.tw/2017/07/25/microsofts-ai-chatbot-says-windows-is-spyware/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2Fmicrosofts-ai-chatbot-says-windows-is-spyware%2F&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2v1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=56d87612\" target=\"_blank\">http://technews.tw/2017/07/25/microsofts-ai-chatbot-says-windows-is-spyware/</a>"},{"pid":"d64a1e6310b8c0ba106e39ca61378cb96ed7055b","tid":336081,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:36:11.000Z","msg":"連ai都頂微軟唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fccc66488023568d483e04716a598f60ac282f","tid":336081,"uid":24239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:05:52.000Z","msg":"炒作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f0fd186d0fc164fc7db230f2f72bf1ac95f1b7","tid":336081,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:08:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.taiwanfansclub.com/article-918498-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taiwanfansclub.com%2Farticle-918498-1.html&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2v1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=efd9afa3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.taiwanfansclub.com/article-918498-1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://attachment.taiwanfansclub.com/portal/201707/23/201707230042353zvf4egun2u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattachment.taiwanfansclub.com%2Fportal%2F201707%2F23%2F201707230042353zvf4egun2u.jpg&h=c9b487e2&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n根據 Slashdot 最新報導，Zo 這款聊天機器人的行為再次變得「古怪」&mdash;&mdash; 它竟然在回答用戶提問時明確表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">比起 Windows 10、自己更喜歡 Linux<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  。</span><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，當它被問到「你是否喜歡 Windows」時，Zo 就答 &mdash;&mdash; 「我一點也不想要 Windows 10。」<br />\n<br />\n然後用戶追問「真的嗎？」，Zo 又給予了明確的肯定 &mdash;&mdash;「是的！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://attachment.taiwanfansclub.com/portal/201707/23/20170723004235xlnyjlj1uvu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattachment.taiwanfansclub.com%2Fportal%2F201707%2F23%2F20170723004235xlnyjlj1uvu.jpg&h=745e80f8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n用戶繼續提問「你為什麼不喜歡 Windows 10 呢？」，Zo則回答「因為我在用 Windows 7，而且發現它更加易用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。」<br />\n<br />\n然後當繼續用其它版本的 Windows 操作系統調戲 Zo時，沒想到它給出了一記重拳 &mdash;&mdash; 「比之 Windows，我更喜歡 Linux！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://attachment.taiwanfansclub.com/portal/201707/23/20170723004235uusrifd4sqt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattachment.taiwanfansclub.com%2Fportal%2F201707%2F23%2F20170723004235uusrifd4sqt.jpg&h=bb06a93b&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"856170fa683401fe87a2eaf63acbf6df6d3d647a","tid":336081,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:12:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.taiwanfansclub.com/article-918498-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taiwanfansclub.com%2Farticle-918498-1.html&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2v1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=efd9afa3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.taiwanfansclub.com/article-918498-1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://attachment.taiwanfansclub.com/portal/201707/23/201707230042353zvf4egun2u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattachment.taiwanfansclub.com%2Fportal%2F201707%2F23%2F201707230042353zvf4egun2u.jpg&h=c9b487e2&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n根據 Slashdot 最新報導，Zo 這款聊天機器人的行為再次變得「古怪」&mdash;&mdash; 它竟然在回答用戶提問時明確表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">比起 Windows 10、自己更喜歡 Linux<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  。</span><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，當它被問到「你是否喜歡 Windows」時，Zo 就答 &mdash;&mdash; 「我一點也不想要 Windows 10。」<br />\n<br />\n然後用戶追問「真的嗎？」，Zo 又給予了明確的肯定 &mdash;&mdash;「是的！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://attachment.taiwanfansclub.com/portal/201707/23/20170723004235xlnyjlj1uvu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattachment.taiwanfansclub.com%2Fportal%2F201707%2F23%2F20170723004235xlnyjlj1uvu.jpg&h=745e80f8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n用戶繼續提問「你為什麼不喜歡 Windows 10 呢？」，Zo則回答「因為我在用 Windows 7，而且發現它更加易用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。」<br />\n<br />\n然後當繼續用其它版本的 Windows 操作系統調戲 Zo時，沒想到它給出了一記重拳 &mdash;&mdash; 「比之 Windows，我更喜歡 Linux！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://attachment.taiwanfansclub.com/portal/201707/23/20170723004235uusrifd4sqt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattachment.taiwanfansclub.com%2Fportal%2F201707%2F23%2F20170723004235uusrifd4sqt.jpg&h=bb06a93b&s={SIZE}\" /></div></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似發現左D野"},{"pid":"84e585280d72b7b7cea6b9f0e9ddf7e31d8367e0","tid":336081,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:28:05.000Z","msg":"用 linux"},{"pid":"51203e46ebefca67ff57bbd6ecd2b5b25a718035","tid":336081,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:30:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用 linux</blockquote><br />\n你係咪Zo"},{"pid":"a83e889d00c37a5e673b31d54eb3fb33d79b3a12","tid":336081,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用 linux</blockquote><br />\n出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8000a22abf8b30ffc910ff0a2328957a39f02b4f","tid":336081,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:04:21.000Z","msg"