load/2017/08/03/112117_a8fd94d3accac8725073c68f83c18111.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F112117_a8fd94d3accac8725073c68f83c18111.jpg&h=67ad4d70&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過mac，試過windows機，都係linux desktop好</blockquote><br />\nMac DE 係幾靚o既,但得copy &amp; paste, 冇cut &amp; paste, 超級唔方便囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用 mouse drag and drop files (with command key) 咪得"},{"pid":"3d7765eab3b3ddd8551b198f92b8d6f4ed5cd982","tid":336081,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:05:40.000Z","msg":"Windows 10成個系統都弱智"},{"pid":"94dd6785c639507665794109d0784a51398910f8","tid":336081,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:29:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Windows 10成個系統都弱智</blockquote><br />\n岩晒d用家"}]}